Title: Island Flotsam
RewardText:
<Jani sniffs the air, smelling your wet garbage.>

Ya brought ol' Jani a present! What ya got there? Let me see it.

<Jani begins rooting through the pile of trash you have brought.>

Oh, yes, and some of this, mmm, mmmhm, yes, oh that's sticky...

<Jani seems pleased with your offering, and is paying no attention to you any longer.>
